subject re john franco jason lee ask what s with john franco the met ar hardli us him i heard he wa complet recov but now i m not so sure you must have heard wrong hi arm is still sore he hasn t gone on the dl but he mai managmenet is treat him as a dai to dai situat hi doctor thought that he wa readi and thei had him throw in colorado but hi arm wasn t up to the strain he is throw everi dai but he s just not quit readi to pitch full strength yet thi is base on an interview that he gave on wfan ny radio on thursdai jon lyon jon k lyon att com at t bell laboratori att jon k lyon 